ActPreclearance Act, 2016
SubjectOrder Fixing the Date on which the Preclearance Act, 2016 Comes into Force as the Day on which the Agreement on Land, Rail, Marine and Air Transport Preclearance between the Government of Canada and the Government of the United States of America Enters into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the date on which the Agreement on Land, Rail, Marine and Air Transport Preclearance between the Government of Canada and the Government of the United States of America comes into force as the day on which the PRECLEARANCE ACT, 2016, chapter 27 of the Statutes of Canada, 2017, COME INTO FORCE.
